gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.render.wave

Class SpectrogramRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.render.FrameRenderer
      • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.render.ImageDataRenderer
        • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.render.wave.SpectrogramRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Renderer, Transformer

    public class SpectrogramRenderer
extends ImageDataRenderer
    Renderer to draw spectrograms. Keeps reference to processed wave data, compute spectrograms and create image to render as ImageDataRenderer.
    Author:
    Dan Cervelli
